{"tid":1376124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個小小嘅非專業提議","createTime":"2019-07-28T08:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T10:42:32.000Z","uid":220743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"012cc9e54ceb99f7fb8988f7406a525ba90cea45","tid":1376124,"uid":220743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"首先小妹並非前線，非戰術撚，軍師都唔係，平日和理非出嚟行同做文宣喺fb share啲post。不過呢段時間有睇過唔少po講啲手足戰友撤退時返屋企驚被狗逗所以掉撚晒啲安全帽剩咁，而且喺街度帶住個黃色安全帽一嚟唔方便收藏二嚟都幾明顯，眼罩呢啲細細個收喺背囊就得，但安全帽呢？<br />\n<br />\n小妹窮撚一個平日行開淘寶，發現淘寶上面有唔少防身用品出售，其中就有輕便型安全帽：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nefVKN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nefVKN.jpg&h=5294b486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaJP0bt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaJP0bt.jpg&h=cc04ba19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZkZSXX9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZkZSXX9.jpg&h=8763a4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外表係一頂普通cap帽但入面有個防撞殼，可拆，戴住佢冇咁容易被狗逗，又方便收藏，唔貴40蚊港紙有找。<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有一款係折疊式安全帽：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqNdHqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqNdHqx.jpg&h=c14a0a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTPjCYT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVTPjCYT.jpg&h=b7544b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然防護性能成疑，不過覺得可以買嚟試吓（本人都諗住買返個保障人身安全），貴啲啲百幾蚊一頂。<br />\n<br />\n同埋之前有巴絲講過帶行山杖、相機腳架等做防具，小妹喺淘寶睇到有隻戰術筆，就咁睇係一支普通嘅筆，但有電筒、刀仔等功能，仲可以真係用嚟寫字，百零蚊一支幾實用：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEk62t5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEk62t5.jpg&h=27219855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENMmRnr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENMmRnr.jpg&h=257647d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然講喺淘寶買好似係俾錢大陸人賺，但如果真係有用嘅話買大陸人嘅嚟對抗港共政府咁樣唔係幾好咩？以上僅僅係個人意見，如有錯誤歡迎指出，謝絕人身攻擊，記住我地槍口係一致對外。<br />\n<br />\n連結：<br />\n安全cap帽 <a href=\"https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.2&amp;id=45171525509&amp;item_id=45171525509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fspm%3Da21wu.11154615-hk.list.2%26id%3D45171525509%26item_id%3D45171525509&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=55cf0242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.2&amp;id=45171525509&amp;item_id=45171525509</a><br />\n折疊安全帽 <a href=\"https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.2&amp;id=579993100084&amp;item_id=579993100084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fspm%3Da21wu.11154615-hk.list.2%26id%3D579993100084%26item_id%3D579993100084&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=450335a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.2&amp;id=579993100084&amp;item_id=579993100084</a><br />\n多功能戰術筆<a href=\"https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.3&amp;id=588645220629&amp;item_id=588645220629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fspm%3Da21wu.11154615-hk.list.3%26id%3D588645220629%26item_id%3D588645220629&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=7848a5d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?spm=a21wu.11154615-hk.list.3&amp;id=588645220629&amp;item_id=588645220629</a>"},{"pid":"d72f210c7894813d3789f4481949847fa4a25662","tid":1376124,"uid":105394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"淘寶都唔賣落黎香港啦"},{"pid":"9f54cd8351478011a38740e974a7b9c4e567599d","tid":1376124,"uid":105394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:20:11.000Z","m